hormonal product melatonin were arrived at on an independent route again. While 
melatonin as a drug has been used on human volunteers for decades, its 
anti-aging effect has yet to be proved. Detailed hormone profiles in different 
age groups and under different life styles have to be performed. A modified 
Hayflick in vitro experiment is also needed to elucidate the mechanism by which 
melatonin works in cells.

